transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Executive: Haan ji sir.
Customer: Sir ji main M.A. Marble Art se baat kar raha tha.
Executive: Uh, so ek minute sir, hold kariyega.
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello, aawaz aa rahi hai sir?
Customer: Haan ji sir, kahan se baat kar rahe hain?
Executive: Haan.
Customer: M.A. Marble Art se baat kar raha tha, Mohammad Makrana Rajasthan se.
Executive: Haan, bataiye.
Customer: Sir, mere jo buyer aa rahe hain mere paas, main jab lead utha raha hun to buyer ke number show kyun nahi ho rahe sir?
Executive: Buyer ke number show nahi ho rahe? Kaise show nahi ho pa rahe usme?
Customer: Matlab ek sirf email ID aa rahi hai, buyer ke number nahi aa rahe mere paas, contact number.
Executive: Ek baar aap company naam batayenge sir mere ko?
Customer: M.A. Marble Art.
Executive: Haan, ek minute. Just a minute.
Executive: Haan ji Marble Art na sir?
Customer: M.A.
Executive: Haan, M.A.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Thik hai, thik hai, thik hai, main ek baar check kar le raha hun sir aapke. M.A. Marble Art.
Executive: Haan ji, haan ji sir, maine sun liya. M for monthly wala M, M.A.
Customer: Haan, haan, A for apple wala.
Executive: Sir, but aapke paas to mera number tha na personal number, aapne mere ko bolne ki aapne customer number pe call kiya hai, right?
Customer: Haan, nahi wo maine customer care number ko number show nahi hue the aapke. Isliye nahi hue the isliye maine customer care pe call kiya tha.
Executive: Achha, achha, achha, achha.
Executive: Thik hai sir. To ye aapko kya problem aa rahi hai main aapko bataun?
Customer: Sir, ye buyer ke number contact number show nahi ho rahe mere paas.
Executive: Uh, aap mere ko ek baar screen share kar sakte hain, main aapko video meet link bhej raha hun. Aap please usko join kariye aur mujhe ek baar screen share karke dikhayenge sir?
Customer: Kaise matlab main samjha nahi, aapko screenshot bhej du?
Executive: Main, main ye, main keh raha hun aapko main video meet ka link bhej raha hun, aap ek baar usko join kariye to main aapko easily main aapko aasani se hum log discuss kar payenge. Thik hai?
Customer: Main nahi samajh paunga sir usko, YouTube pe main already karta hun. Mera jo kaam karta hai worker bachcha wo aaya nahi aaj isliye main nahi samajh paunga aap jo bhi bologe.
Executive: Aap, main bata dunga sir kaise dikhate hain.
Customer: Achha.
Executive: Haan.
Executive: Sir, aapko aapko dikha lo na aapke buyer show show kyun nahi kar raha hai?
Customer: Sir main solution ke liye hi aapko call karne ke liye keh raha hun. Solution hi nikalunga sir se. Like aapko ek baar call uthaiye to phir usko ek baar. Aap ek baar usko join kariye main bata raha hun. Aapko maine mail ID bhi bheji hai, aap ek baar check kariye.
Executive: Kis naam se video call jo aa raha hai?
Executive: Haan, IndiaMART ke mere Sameeksha naam se aa rahi hogi, IndiaMART.com se maine aapko bheji hai sir. Isko yes, isko yes karu?
Executive: Haan ji sir, isko yes kariye aur joining video meet kar lijiye.
Customer: Yes, yes kar diya maine, join karu?
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Haan, join ho gaya.
Executive: Aap jis vyakti se baat kar rahe hain, unhone aapke call ko [unintelligible]
